Global Sportfishing Yachts Market Insights
Sportfishing Yachts Market size was valued at USD 3.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.6% from 2024 to 2030.

Sportfishing Yachts Market Overview
The global sportfishing yachts market is estimated to be valued at approximately USD 6.2 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of around 5.6% during the forecast period. Increasing popularity of recreational fishing, high demand for luxury yachts, and advancements in yacht design and technology contribute to this steady market growth. The rising preference for outdoor activities, coupled with a growing affluent population seeking high-end recreational experiences, is driving the sportfishing yachts market's expansion across global regions. North America and Europe hold significant shares due to established yacht manufacturing hubs and the presence of high-income consumers in these regions.

